  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtendedList<T>
    This class extends ArrayList to provide additional useful functionalities.
    ExtendedListTest
    Test methods from ExtendedList.
    MazeMath
    This class provides useful methods to operate on to arrays/lists and convert between the directional systems of Floorplan, Distance, CardinalDirection, Robot.Direction and Robot.Turn, which can be used by other classes without hassle.
    MazeMathTest
    Test methods from MazeMath.
    RobotMove
    Provides a mechanism to move a robot by a certain distance.
    RobotOperation
    This class is extended by classes that operate on a robot.
    RobotOperationTracker
    This class tracks a series of operations to be performed by a Robot, and can instruct the robot to perform those operations.
    RobotRotation
    Provides a mechanism to move a robot by a certain distance.
